# Aegis is BYOK: model provider API keys are entered and encrypted in the extension's
# vault UI at runtime. They are never read from environment variables and never
# committed to the repo.
#
# The variables below are optional and only used for manual/local runs of the
# reliability eval harness in "live" mode. Vitest unit tests never require any of
# these, and CI never sets them.

# OPENAI_API_KEY=
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# GOOGLE_GENERATIVE_AI_API_KEY=
